">(Loco featuring Jay Park)</span>\n**\"Mommae\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Jay Park featuring Ugly Duck)</span>\n**\"You Know\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Jay Park featuring Okasian)</span>\n**\"Ain't No Party Like An AOMG Party\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Jay Park & Ugly Duck)</span>\n**\"Me Like Yuh (K)\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Jay Park featuring Hoody)</span>\n\n== Discography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Year\n!Album title\n!Artist\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2013\n|''Call Me Gray''\n|[[Gray (singer)|Gray]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20131208000170|title=Producer-turned-rapper wants everyone to know his name|last=Kalka|first=Emma|date=2013-12-08|website=The Korea Herald|language=en|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2014\n|''Evolution''\n|[[Jay Park]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/6243940/jay-park-evolution-album-so-good-promise|title=Jay Park Showcases His Rapping & Singing 'Evolution' on Strong Sophomore LP|last=Oak|first=Jessica|last2=Benjamin|first2=Jeff|date=2014-09-06|website=Billboard|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Locomotive''\n|[[Loco (rapper)|Loco]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.joins.com/article/22491292|title=\ub85c\uaf2c, \ub370\ubdd4 \uccab \ub2e8\ub3c5 \ucf58\uc11c\ud2b8 \ud2f0\ucf13 \uc624\ud508 1\ubd84 \ub9cc\uc5d0 \uc804\uc11d \ub9e4\uc9c4|date=2018-03-30|website=JoongAng Ilbo|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2015\n|''Won & Only''\n|[[Simon Dominic]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/641103|title=\uc0ac\uc774\uba3c \ub3c4\ubbf8\ub2c9, '\uc6d0\uc564\uc628\ub9ac'\ub85c \uc74c\uc6d0 \ucc28\ud2b8 \uc811\uc218 '2\uc5f0\ud0c0 \ud648\ub7f0'|date=2015-08-21|website=Ten Asia|language=ko-KR|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Worldwide''\n|Jay Park\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cctoday.co.kr/?mod=news&act=articleView&idxno=935877|title=\ubc15\uc7ac\ubc94 \uc0c8\uc568\ubc94\uc740 \ud799\ud569 \ucef4\ud544\ub808\uc774\uc158?\u2026\ub798\ud37c 27\uba85 \ud53c\ucc98\ub9c1|date=2015-10-30|website=Chungcheong Today|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2016\n|''Scene Stealers''\n|Jay Park & [[Ugly Duck (rapper)|Ugly Duck]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.asiatoday.co.kr/view.php?key=20160712001122059|title=\ubc15\uc7ac\ubc94X\uc5b4\uae00\ub9ac\ub355, \u2018\uc6b0\ub9ac\uac00 \ube60\uc9c0\uba74 PARTY\uac00 \uc544\ub2c8\uc9c0\u2019 \uacf5\uac1c\u2026AOMG \ucf5c\ub77c\ubcf4|date=2016-07-13|website=Asia Today|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''8 Femmes''\n|[[Elo (singer)|Elo]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/news/entertain/view/2016/08/597829/|title=ELO(\uc5d8\ub85c), \ubc15\uc7ac\ubc94\uacfc \ud568\uaed8\ud55c \u2018\ud0c0\ud22c(Tattoo)\u2019 \uc120\uacf5\uac1c|date=2016-08-23|website=Maeil Business Newspaper|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Everything You Wanted''\n|Jay Park\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nocutnews.co.kr/news/4667142|title=\ubc15\uc7ac\ubc94, 20\uc77c \uc0c8 \uc815\uaddc \uc568\ubc94 \ubc1c\ub9e4 \u2018AOMG \ucd1d\ucd9c\ub3d9\u2019|date=2016-10-11|website=No Cut News|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''On and On''\n|[[Hoody (singer)|Hoody]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/7655483/new-k-pop-artists-to-watch-2017|title=Top 5 K-Pop Artists to Watch in 2017|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|last2=Herman|first2=Tamar|date=2017-01-19|website=Billboard|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|''Bleached''\n|Loco\n|<ref name=\":4\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/news/home/view/2018/11/738865/|title=\ub798\ud37c \ub85c\uaf2c, \ub0b4\ub144 2\uc6d4 7\uc77c \uc758\ubb34\uacbd\ucc30 \uc785\ub300 - \ub9e4\uc77c\uacbd\uc81c|date=2018-11-26|website=Maeil Business Newspaper|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Summer Go Loco''\n|Loco\n|<ref name=\":4\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2018\n|''Darkroom''\n|Simon Dominic\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/1513821|title=\uc0ac\uc774\uba3c \ub3c4\ubbf8\ub2c9, \uc0c8 \uc568\ubc94 'DARKROOM: roommates only' \uc624\ub298(15\uc77c) \uacf5\uac1c|date=2018-06-15|website=Ten Asia|language=ko-KR|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Ask Bout Me''\n|Jay Park\n|<ref name=\":3\" />\n|-\n|''af''\n|[[Woo Won-jae]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20181119075800005|title=\uc6b0\uc6d0\uc7ac, 22\uc77c \uccab \ubbf8\ub2c8\uc568\ubc94\u2026\ud0c0\uc774\ud2c0\uace1\uc740 '\uc6b8\ud0c0\ub9ac'|date=2018-11-19|website=Yonhap News|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2019\n|''Hello''\n|Loco\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/2019020638554|title=\ub85c\uaf2c \uc785\ub300 \uc804 \ub9c8\uc9c0\ub9c9 \uc568\ubc94 \ud0c0\uc774\ud2c0\uace1 '\uc624\ub79c\ub9cc\uc774\uc57c', \ud2f0\uc800 \uacf5\uac1c|date=2019-02-06|website=Korea Economic Daily|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''No Open Flames''\n|Simon Dominic\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hiphopkr.com/news/music-release/simon-dominic-no-open-flames-ep/|title=SIMON DOMINIC DROPS \u201cNO OPEN FLAMES\u201d EP AND \u201cGOTT\u201d MV|date=2019-09-03|website=HIPHOPKR|language=en|access-date=2019-11-05}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Departure''\n|Hoody\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dkhhrnb.com/2019/10/30/hoody-departure/|title=Hoody Departure Album 1st Full album of AOMG Hoody|date=2019-10-30|website=DKhhrnb|language=en|access-date=2019-11-05}}</ref>\n|-\n|''ODD''\n|Elo x [[Penomeco|Penomeco]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aomgofficial.lnk.to/ODD|title='LOVE? (Feat. GRAY)' ELO x PENOMECO, EP [ODD]|date=2019-11-07|website=AOMG Official|language=ko|access-date=2019-11-07}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Tours ==\n'''AOMG 2014 United States Tour'''\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Date\n