ly|language=ko|access-date=2019-04-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|''No Open Flames''\n|Simon Dominic\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hiphopkr.com/news/music-release/simon-dominic-no-open-flames-ep/|title=SIMON DOMINIC DROPS \u201cNO OPEN FLAMES\u201d EP AND \u201cGOTT\u201d MV|date=2019-09-03|website=HIPHOPKR|language=en|access-date=2019-11-05}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Departure''\n|Hoody\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dkhhrnb.com/2019/10/30/hoody-departure/|title=Hoody Departure Album 1st Full album of AOMG Hoody|date=2019-10-30|website=DKhhrnb|language=en|access-date=2019-11-05}}</ref>\n|-\n|''ODD''\n|Elo x [[Penomeco|Penomeco]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aomgofficial.lnk.to/ODD|title='LOVE? (Feat. GRAY)' ELO x PENOMECO, EP [ODD]|date=2019-11-07|website=AOMG Official|language=ko|access-date=2019-11-07}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Tours ==\n'''AOMG 2014 United States Tour'''\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Date\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|City\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Country\n! style=\"width:250px;\"|Venue\n|-\n|14 November 2014\n|[[Los Angeles]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |United States'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/6274257/jay-park-aomg-us-tour-simon-d-gray-loco-dj-pumpkin|title=Jay Park to Head Out on AOMG U.S. Tour With Simon D, Gray, Loco & DJ Pumpkin|date=2014-10-14|website=Billboard|access-date=2016-03-25}}</ref>'''\n|Belasco Theater\n|-\n|15 November 2014\n|[[New York City|New York]]\n|Stage 48\n|-\n|20 November 2014\n|[[Washington, D.C.]]\n|[[Echostage]]\n|}\n'''Follow The Movement Tour 2016'''\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Date\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|City\n! style=\"width:150px;\"|Country\n! style=\"width:250px;\"|Venue\n|-\n|29 January 2016\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Seoul]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |South Korea<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/822608|title=\ud799\ud569 \ub808\uc774\ube14 AOMG, \uccab \ub2e8\ub3c5 \uc