om/2016/04/14/a-dozen-armored-cars-better-than-the-humvee/#more-205396|title=A Dozen Armored Cars Better Than The Humvee|date=April 14, 2016|publisher=|accessdate=August 15, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Otokar Cobra]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Otokar Cobra APC. (33618763016).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Infantry mobility vehicle]]\n| {{flag|Turkey}}\n| 280{{citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n| The 20 received in 2017 are the [[Otokar Cobra II]]<ref name=\"SIPRI\" /> and 250 received between mid of 2019 .{{citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n|-\n| [[BOV M11]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army BOV M11 armored reconnaissance vehicle. (32305980000).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Armored reconnaissance vehicle]]\n| {{flag|Serbia}}\n| 20\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kurir-info.rs/poceo-izvoz-borbenih-vozila-clanak-834583|title=Po\u010deo izvoz borbenih vozila|language=Serbian|publisher=Kurir|date=11 June 2013|accessdate=17 June 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[RN-94]]\n| [[File:Transportor RN94 amfibiu blindat de cercetare.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier#Medical use|Armored ambulance]]\n| {{flag|Romania}}\n| 9\n| Delivered in 2005.<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[BTR-80]]\n| [[File:BTR-80 of Bangladesh Army.png|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier]]\n| [[File:Flag of the Soviet Union.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[Soviet Union]]<p>{{flag|Russia}}\n| 645-1030(sources vary)\n|<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[Type 85 AFV|Type 85 Armored Command Vehicle]]\n| [[File:ChineseType85C2Veh.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier]]\n| {{CHN}}\n| 50\n| <ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|}\n\n==Engineering Vehicles==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Name\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=15%| Type\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Quantity\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n| [[Type 84|Type 653]] || [[File:Bangladesh Army Norinco Type 653 ARV (27278354632).jpg|150px]] ||[[Armoured recovery vehicle]]  || [[File:Flag of the People's Republic of China.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]] || 5 |