a.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 132\n| {{sfn|The Military Balance 2016|p=236}}\n|-\n| [[AZP S-60|Type-59]]\n| [[File:S-60.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Autocannon|57mm Autocannon]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 34\n| According to ''The Military Balance 2017'' by [[International Institute for Strategic Studies|IISS]]{{sfn|The Military Balance 2017|p=274}} \n|-\n| [[Oerlikon GDF#Versions|Oerlikon GDF]]\n| [[File:GDF Ej\u00e9rcito espa\u00f1ol.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Autocannon|35mm Autocannon]]\n| {{SWI}}\n| 4\n| GDF-009 variant.<ref name=\"auto2\">{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=NEWLY ADDITION IN BANGLADESH ARMY ORELIKON RADAR CONTROLLED GUN TEST FIRING HELD AT COXBAZAR|url=https://www.ispr.gov.bd/en/newly-addition-in-bangladesh-army-orelikon-radar-controlled-gun-test-firing-held-at-coxbazar/#pll_switcher|language=Bangla|work=ISPR |location=Bangladesh |date=13 October 2019 |access-date=14 October 2019}}</ref> 2 system more on order with skyguard radar.{{citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n|}\n\n==Radars==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Name\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=15%| Type\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Quantity\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n| [[SLC-2 Radar|SLC-2]]|| [[File:Bangladesh Army SLC-2 weapon locating Radar (25040973326).jpg|150px]] || [[Counter-battery radar]] || {{flag|China}} || ||{{citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n|-\n| [[Oerlikon GDF#Skyguard|Skyguard]]|| [[File:FLGer98 Skyguard.JPG|150px]] || [[Fire-control radar]] || {{SWI}} ||\n|For [[Oerlikon GDF]]<ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n|}\n\n==Watercraft==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Class\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=25%| Ships\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Displacement\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n| Shakti Sanchar class [[Landing craft tank|LCT]]\n|[[File:Bangladesh Army LCT Shakti Sanchar (29505122891).jpg|150px]]\n| LCT Shakti Sanchar\n| [[File:Flag of Bangladesh.svg|frameless|23x23px]