adesh Army KIA Cerato staff-car (29124211206).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of South Korea.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[South Korea]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Lancer#Facelift|Mitsubishi Lancer EX]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army facelifted Mitsubishi Lancer EX staff-car. (30086525537).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Lancer#Asia|Mitsubishi Lancer GLX]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi Lancer GLX staff car (24810466834).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Nissan Sunny#N16 (2000\u20132005)|Nissan Sunny N16]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Nissan Sunny N16 staff-car (29448969845).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Corolla (E140)#E150 wide-body|Toyota Corolla E150]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Corolla E150 staff car (24814294683).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Corolla (E100)|Toyota Corolla E100]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Corolla E100 staff-car. (34533108752).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Delica|Mitsubishi L300]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi L300 ambulance. (24600352466).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Land Cruiser]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Land Cruiser 70 ambulance. (31366598591).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Toyota HiAce#Fourth generation (H100; 1989\u20132004)|Toyota HiAce]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota HiAce H100 Ambulance (23328585980).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Volkswagen Crafter]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army VW Crafter ambulance (24240660240).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulan