 older versions.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://camopedia.org/index.php?title=Bangladesh|title=Bangladesh|work=Camopedia}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Bangladesh Army]]\n* [[East Bengal Regiment]]\n* [[Bangladesh Infantry Regiment]]\n* [[Bangladesh Army Aviation Group]]\n* [[List of active Bangladesh military aircraft]]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n* {{cite book|title=The Military Balance 2016|date=February 2016|volume=116|isbn=9781857438352 |publisher=Routlegde|ref={{harvid|The Military Balance 2016}}|author=International Institute for Strategic Studies|author-link=International Institute for Strategic Studies}}\n\n== External links ==\n\n{{Commons category|Equipment of the Bangladesh Army}}\n* [http://www.army.mil.bd/ Official Website of Bangladesh Army]\n* [http://lcweb2.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/r?frd/cstdy:@field(DOCID+bd0150) Library of Congress Country Studies assessment of Bangladesh Army (1988)]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120908115236/http://articles.janes.com/articles/Janes-Armour-and-Artillery/Yugoimport-NORA-B-52-155-mm-52-calibre-self-propelled-gun-Serbia.html Janes.com]\n* [http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/bangladesh/army-equipment.htm www.globalsecurity.org]\n* [http://www.bof.gov.bd/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=83&Itemid=212 http://www.bof.gov.bd]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150513023233/http://www.bmtf.com.bd/special-vehicles/ www.bmtf.com.bd]\n\n{{Military of Bangladesh}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Equipment of the Bangladesh Army}}\n[[Category:Military equipment of Bangladesh]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2017}}\n{{EngvarB|date=March 2017}}\n{{more citations needed|date=September 2019}}\n'''Equipment of the Bangladesh Army''' is a list of the equipment currently in use in the [[Bangladesh Army]]. It includes small arms, vehicles, artillery, and aircraft.\n[[File:Roundel of Bangladesh - Army Aviation.svg|200px|thumb|right|Emblem of Bangladesh Army]]\n\n== Small arms ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"wid