 borbenih vozila|language=Serbian|publisher=Kurir|date=11 June 2013|accessdate=17 June 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[RN-94]]\n| [[File:Transportor RN94 amfibiu blindat de cercetare.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier#Medical use|Armored ambulance]]\n| {{flag|Romania}}\n| 9\n| Delivered in 2005.<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[BTR-80]]\n| [[File:BTR-80 of Bangladesh Army.png|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier]]\n| [[File:Flag of the Soviet Union.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[Soviet Union]]<p>{{flag|Russia}}\n| 645-1030(sources vary)\n|<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[Type 85 AFV|Type 85 Armored Command Vehicle]]\n| [[File:ChineseType85C2Veh.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Armoured personnel carrier]]\n| {{CHN}}\n| 50\n| <ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|}\n\n==Engineering Vehicles==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Name\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=15%| Type\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Quantity\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n| [[Type 84|Type 653]] || [[File:Bangladesh Army Norinco Type 653 ARV (27278354632).jpg|150px]] ||[[Armoured recovery vehicle]]  || [[File:Flag of the People's Republic of China.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]] || 5 || 5 Type 653 [[Armoured recovery vehicle|ARV]] received in 1993 and 3 Type 654 in 2012.<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| [[BTR-80|BREM-K]] || [[File:BREM-K(BTR-80 ARV) Bangladesh Army (23587740026).jpg|150px]] || [[Armoured recovery vehicle]] || [[File:Flag of the People's Republic of China.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]  || 10+ || In 2011 Bangladesh received 80 BTR-80s including unknown numbers of ARV.In 2016-17 Bangladesh received 340 BTR-80s Including 10 ARV version.<ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| Type 79A || [[File:Bangladesh Army Type 79A ribbon bridge on Tiema XC2200 truck. (31288481070).jpg|150px]] ||[[Pontoon bridge]] ||  [[File:Flag of the People's Republic of China.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]] || ||\n|-\n|-valign=\"top\"\n| Grove TM 750E || [[File:Bangladesh Army Grove TM 750E crane (24938250945).jpg|150px]] || [[Crane (machine)|Crane]] ||  [[File:Flag of the United States.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[United States]] || ||\n|}\n\n==Artillery==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Name\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=15%| Type\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Quantity\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\"| [[Self-Propelled Artillery]]\n|-\n| [[Nora B-52]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Nora B-52 155mm SPG (31586399521).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Self-propelled gun|155 mm self-propelled gun]]\n| [[File:Flag of Serbia.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[Serbia]]\n| 36\n| <ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[Weishi Rockets#WS-22|WS-22]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army WS-22 MLRS. (33659597465).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Self-propelled artillery#Rockets and missiles|122 mm Self-propelled rocket launcher]]<br>[[Rocket artillery]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 72{{citation needed|date=September 2019}}\n|<ref name=\"SIPRI\" /><ref name=\"Shakil Bin Mushtaq\"/>\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\"| [[Field artillery|Towed Artillery]]\n|-\n|-\n| [[130 mm towed field gun M1954 (M-46)|Type 59-1]]\n| [[File:Iraqi Type 59 130 mm field gun.JPEG|150px]]\n| [[Field gun|130 mm Field gun]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 62\n| <ref name=\"Arty2016\"/><ref name=\"SIPRI\" />\n|-\n| [[122 mm howitzer 2A18 (D-30)|Type 96]]\n| [[File:122- \u043c\u043c \u0433\u0430\u0443\u0431\u0438\u0446\u0430 \u0414-30 (1).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Howitzer|122 mm Howitzer]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 54\n| <ref name=\"Arty2016\"/>\n|-\n| [[122 mm howitzer M1938 (M-30)|Type 54/Type 54-1]]\n| [[File:VDVHistorymuseum-21.jpg|150px]]\n| [[Howitzer|122mm Field Howitzer]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 57\n| <ref name=\"Arty2016\"/>\n|-\n| Type-83\n| [[File:No-image-available.png|150px]]\n| [[Howitzer|122 mm Howitzer]]\n| [[File:Flag of China.png|frameless|23x23px]] [[China]]\n| 20\n| <r