0150723123505/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/bangladesh/army-arms.htm |archive-date=23 July 2015 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=3 July 2013 |title=Army helicopter crashes |url=http://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2013/07/03/army-helicopter-crashes |newspaper=bdnews24.com |access-date=23 July 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312062140/http://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2013/07/03/army-helicopter-crashes |archive-date=12 March 2016 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\"| [[Unmanned Aerial Vehicle]]\n|-\n|[[Bramor C4EYE]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Bramor UAV. (39051236781).jpg|150px]]\n| [[Aerial reconnaissance#Modern technology|Reconnaissance UAV]] \n| [[File:Flag of Slovenia.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Slovenia]]\n| 36\n|  <ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.c-astral.com/en/products/bramor-c4eye| title=Bramor C4EYE| publisher=C-Astral| date=|accessdate=28 May 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Utility Vehicle==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:90%;\"\n|-\n! width=16%| Name\n! width=21%| Image\n! width=15%| Type\n! width=12%| Origin\n! width=10%| Quantity\n! width=26%| Notes\n|-\n| [[Toyota Land Cruiser]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army LC 70 soft-top (24844924921).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Toyota Land Cruiser]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Land Cruiser 70 pickup.jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Pickup Truck\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Land Rover Defender]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Land Rover Defender (24679763581).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| [[File:Flag of the United Kingdom.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[United Kingdom]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[KM131 Jeep|KM 420]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army KIA KM420 (24258817439).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| [[File:Flag of South Korea.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[South Korea]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Triton|Mitsubishi L200]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi L200 (24106881284).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Toyota Hilux]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Hilux (24439534470).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Ford Ranger]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army (G.E) Ford Ranger. (37721331456).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility Vehicle\n| {{flag|United States}}<br>[[File:Flag of Thailand.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Thailand]]\n| \n| Currently manufactured in Thailand\n|-\n| [[Mercedes-Benz C-Class|Mercedes Benz C280]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mercedes Benz C280 staff car. (36866182040).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Germany.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Germany]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Pajero]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi Pajero 4th gen.jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| 4th gen.\n|-\n| [[Toyota Camry (XV40)|Toyota Camry XV40]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Camry XV40 staff car (27923240034).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Kia Cerato|KIA Cerato]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army KIA Cerato staff-car (29124211206).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of South Korea.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[South Korea]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Lancer#Facelift|Mitsubishi Lancer EX]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army facelifted Mitsubishi Lancer EX staff-car. (30086525537).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Lancer#Asia|Mitsubishi Lancer GLX]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi Lancer GLX staff car (24810466834).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Nissan Sunny#N16 (2000\u20132005)|Nissan Sunny N16]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Nissan Sunny N16 staff-car (29448969845).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Corolla (E140)#E150 wide-body|Toyota Corolla E150]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Corolla E150 staff car (24814294683).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Corolla (E100)|Toyota Corolla E100]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota Corolla E100 staff-car. (34533108752).jpg|150px]]\n| Staff Car\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Mitsubishi Delica|Mitsubishi L300]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mitsubishi L300 ambulance. (24600352466).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| [[Toyota Land Cruiser]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Land Cruiser 70 ambulance. (31366598591).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Toyota HiAce#Fourth generation (H100; 1989\u20132004)|Toyota HiAce]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Toyota HiAce H100 Ambulance (23328585980).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| [[Volkswagen Crafter]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army VW Crafter ambulance (24240660240).jpg|150px]]\n| Ambulance\n| [[File:Flag of Germany.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Germany]]\n| \n| \n|-\n| Arunima Bolyan\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Arunima Bolyan 4X4 truck. (39440131174).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility 4x4 truck\n| [[File:Flag of Bangladesh.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Bangladesh]]\n| \n| {{Citation needed|date=May 2019}}\n|-\n| [[Bedford TK|Bedford MJ]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Bedford MJ truck (28855354693).jpg|150px]]\n| Utility 4x4 truck\n| [[File:Flag of the United Kingdom.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[United Kingdom]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| Isuzu TSD-45\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Isuzu TSD-45.jpg|150px]]\n| Utility 4x4 truck\n| [[File:Flag of Japan.svg|frameless|23x23px]] [[Japan]]\n| \n| {{Citation needed|date=May 2019}}\n|-\n| [[ZIL-131]]\n| [[File:Bangladesh Army Mobile Field Bakery System with Zil-137 tractor. (39311044931).jpg|